oth things.<br />But to translate some sentences I need sometimes even 1 entirely day, so I don't have time to study! <br />It's really hard, but I have to follow a book, a workbook, steadly. Something that I start to study from the beginning until the end.<br /><br />There's books that you would suggest me?<br /><br />Thank you a lot again for  the help!</div>

			

